check_compatible_ms_formats_for_conversion

Source: R/fct_ms_001_convert_trim_files_.R
check_compatible_ms_formats_for_conversion.Rd

List of possible vendor formats to be converted to mzML or mzXML.

Usage

check_compatible_ms_formats_for_conversion()

Value

A data.frame with the formats compatible for conversion.
